g.text: Time spent commuting per day (15 min/dot)
Initial Worries: Will I get to school on time?
Level 1 Worries: Will I make either the early or later time?
Level 2 Worries: Will my back-up get me to school on time?
Level 3 Worries: Why did the scheduled vehicle not arrive?How will I get to school now?Will I be tardy to my first class?Will I be able to retake the quiz?...
